OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening otherwise dry.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will be cloudy
OL,8,Fwith occasional rain spreading from
OL,9,Fthe southwest. Freshening wind along
OL,10,Fthe east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,13,Ftime in the morning. The afternoon
OL,14,Fwill be brighter with a few showers.
OL,15,FBrisk southwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,18,Fcloudy on Saturday and Sunday with a
OL,19,Ffew showers, some dry and brighter
OL,20,Fweather too. Chance of further showery
OL,21,Frain on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
